<template><section>

<h2 id="form-biao-dan"><a class="header-anchor" href="#form-biao-dan" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> Form 表单</h2>
<p>由输入框、选择器、单选框、多选框等控件组成，用以收集、校验、提交数据</p>
<h3 id="dian-xing-biao-dan"><a class="header-anchor" href="#dian-xing-biao-dan" aria-hidden="true">¶</a> 典型表单</h3>
<p>包括各种表单项，比如输入框、选择器、开关、单选框、多选框等。</p>
